title: They just keep getting better
body: <a href="http://www.animationinsider.net/modules.php?module=article&amp;id=190">Cartoon Network Ranks Highest Week Ever</a> - "... Cartoon Network's late night block, "<a title="Adult Swim" href="http://www.adultswim.com" >Adult Swim</a>" controls the ratings for ages 18-34 and 18-24. Family Guy has a lot to celebrate about, as well. A week of Family Guy (11 p.m.) featuring creator Seth McFarlane’s opening and closing comments ratings increased among adults 18-34 and adults 18-24, ranking #1 in its time period on basic cable. Its’ ratings went up a whopping 166%. The pilot of new original series Stroker and Hoop (Sunday, 11:30 p.m.) ranked #1 in its time period on basic cable for delivery of adults 18-24. ..."
